text: Forest of the Gods () is a 2005 Lithuanian World War II drama movie directed by Algimantas Puipa and based on the 1957 novel of the same name by Balys Sruoga. It stars Valentinas Masalskis, Steven Berkoff, Liubomiras Laucevičius, Rolandas Boravskis, Šarūnas Puidokas, Robertas Urbonas, Saulius Mykolaitis and Monika Bičiūnaitė. == Other websites == * * Category:2005 drama movies Category:2000s war movies Category:Lithuanian movies Category:British drama movies Category:World War II movies Category:Movies set in Lithuania Category:Movies based on books Category:Movies directed by Algimantas Puipa
